com.ephesoft.dcma.batch.service

Interface XMLSchemaAdapterService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    XMLSchemaAdapterServiceImpl

    public interface XMLSchemaAdapterService
    Service that provides the adapters associated with the specific category of the XML.

    This can be used to fetch the Adapters associated with the different types of XML. For example adapters associated with the HOCR.xml and Batch.XML should be different as they are associated to different types of XSD parameters.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Ephesoft.
